    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small, thin, flat pieces of metal, leather, or other suitable material bearing a unique official identification number of a registered vehicle, to which it is to be attached.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
